column3: Today, I practiced lightsaber combat with Master Yoda. Tough day!
I grow stronger every day. Soon, I will crush the Rebellion.
The next step is to gather allies for the cause. I miss Alderaan.
Another day, another repair on the Millennium Falcon. Why do I keep this thing?
Spent the day hunting on Kashyyyk. Peaceful. Until a Trandoshan showed up.
Meditating on the future. Much fear, I sense.
